---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: About
eyebrow: Background
intro: Backend-focused software engineer with 6+ years of experience, specializing in enterprise systems, Spring Boot microservices, and cloud platforms (AWS/Azure). Currently working on infrastructure in the telecom and public safety domain, based in Tampere, Finland.
permalink: /about/
---
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Experience</span>
      <h2>Where I've worked</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      {% for role in experience %}
      <div class="role">
        <div class="meta">
          <h3>{{ role.title }} — {{ role.company }}</h3>
          <span class="where">{{ role.location }} · {{ role.dates }}</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          {% for bullet in role.bullets %}<li>{{ bullet }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% if role.tech.length %}
        <div class="row-inline tech">
          {% for t in role.tech %}<span class="pill">{{ t }}</span>{% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Skills</span>
      <h2>What I work with</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      {% for skill in skills %}
      <div class="skill-group"><h3>{{ skill.group }}</h3><p>{{ skill.items }}</p></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Education &amp; certification</span>
      <h2>Studies</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="edu">
      {% for item in education.degrees %}
      <div class="card">
        <h3>{{ item.degree }}</h3>
        <p>{{ item.detail }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% if education.certifications.length %}
    <div class="row-inline" style="margin-top:var(--s5)">
      {% for cert in education.certifications %}<span class="pill">{{ cert }}</span>{% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Next step</span>
      <h2>Considering me for a role?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row-inline">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ site.cv }}" download="Ali-Hussain-CV.pdf">Download CV</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.github }}">View GitHub</a>
      <a class="btn btn-text" href="/contact/">Get in touch →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
